even cleaned, have you?!
You're half right, it's a bit painful to hear.
What does the Guild Association do to make a profit?
They take a cut from the middle.

They can't even pass the test.
Leave it to the super sexy Memerisu-chan!
Kid... if you underestimate me, I'll crush you.

I didn't expect you to pass the exam. Sorry about earlier,
please accept this as an apology.

Alright, let's sell this off and use it as funds for our
journey!
Hey!? Please don't say that in front of them!

The monsters in the dungeon may inflict status ailments. Be
careful.

This is the Adventurer's Guild. You'll find wonderful
companions here!
Excuse me, I'd like to try my hand at the dungeon~!

The super beautiful Memerisu-chan and this is Tina-chan, in
charge of boobs.

What are you saying?! I don't remember being in charge of
that!
Oh my, what energetic young ladies.
Ah... I'm sorry. We've caused a commotion...

So, we would like to challenge the dungeon together, but we
heard we need the guild's permission, so we're here about
that...
I see~, so that's what it is.
I'm sorry, but I cannot give permission.

I'd like to give permission, but... there are many strong
monsters in the dungeon and it's dangerous, you know?

Countless adventurers have been dazzled by the dungeon's
treasures and never returned...
It's too reckless for two girls to take on such a place.

Noooooo!!! I need money! Money is necessary for meeee!!!
Money is more important than life itself!!!

...She really wants to go to the dungeon... isn't there
anything we can do?

Hmm... Well... If you two had the skills to take on the
dungeon, there would be no problem granting permission...
Ah! That's right! How about this then?

Actually, there's been a sighting of a thief hiding out in
the forest to the east.

This thief was once an adventurer who had challenged the
dungeon.

If you can catch this skilled thief, I will grant you
permission to enter the dungeon.
I see... so it's like a test!
Okay! We accept that proposal! Let's do it!!
To just accept so readily...!! I'm worried...
Then please do your best I'm rooting for you!
It seems the thief is hiding in the forest to the east.

If you catch the thief, I'll grant you permission to enter
the dungeon.

Good work. I honestly didn't expect you to actually catch a
thief... I'm quite surprised.
Hehe~ Well, when I get serious, this is what happens!

You always get carried away so quickly... You're going to
get hurt one of these days, you know?

Then, as promised, I'll grant you permission to enter the
dungeon. I'll contact the guards, so feel free to challenge
it whenever you like

Also, I'll give you an item that allows you to return to
Utage Village from anywhere, the Utage Wings.

You've obtained the Utage Wings and are now able to
challenge the dungeon!

Alright! The dungeon treasures are calling for me! Let's go
challenge it right away, Tina-chan

Make sure we're fully prepared before heading to the
dungeon, okay!?
Please do your best in challenging the dungeon

Oigorurua! There's no treasure in the dungeon at all?! What
the heck is going on?!
Eek!? What's with the sudden outburst...

Memerisu-chan, please calm down! You're making a face
unbefitting of a heroine!!
Um... Tina-san...? Could you explain in more detail?
I see... So the dungeon's treasure was empty...

Hmm, that's strange. We haven't received any reports of the
dungeon's treasure being collected...

It's possible that thieves or individuals who entered
illegally without going through the guild took the treasure
first... or maybe it was empty from the start...

Noooooo!!! If there's no treasure in the dungeon, what am I
supposed to do about my debt?!

If that's the case, why not try going to another island?
There are dungeons on other islands and I believe there are
undiscovered treasures as well.

I'll give you special permission to use the magic circle
that can transport you to another island. The magic circle
is located next to the dungeon entrance.

No, wait a minute!!!! It's not acceptable to clear a dungeon
and get no reward!!

I'm filing a complaint! I'm going to complain to the
management and express my feelings on SNS!

...Can't be helped. It seems we made a slight mistake this
time, so as a special case, here you go.

Apology stones, yay! The management really is divine! I'll
keep following you guys!

Alright! Now that it's decided, let's set off at once! Our
next target is the treasure of the next island!

The magic circle that can take you to the next island is
right next to the dungeon entrance. Good luck!

By the way, Memerisu-san. I have a very good offer... Are
you interested?
A very good offer!? Tell me more-! I'm all ears-!!

Actually... wouldn't you like to have a stronger weapon to
use on your adventures, something worthy of a comrade?

But as a rookie adventurer, you don't have the jewels for a
strong weapon, right?

Guess what! There's a special campaign for newcomers where
you could win a weapon worth 10,000,000 jewels (company
estimate) for just 300 jewels!

Yes! It's a campaign where you could win something worth
10,000,000 jewels (company estimate)!

Moreover, for 3000 jewels you can do an 8-spin bundle which
is a great deal! (Saves time)

Just 300 jewels for 10,000,000 jewels... That's too good to
be true...!! I've got to go all in!!

Hehehe... I'm glad it piqued your interest. When you want to
participate in the campaign, just talk to me.
